description: Young stars have been criticised after announcing they were abandoning efforts to combat the virus.
title: Dutch celebs face backlash over Covid rebellion
title_page: Dutch celebs face backlash over Covid rebellion - BBC News
maintext: "I'm not sure it meant more people not adhering to the guidelines; maybe it will mean more people do because they're so angry about what these people did. It could go both ways. Influencers distributing these types of things is not good. It's not what we need at the moment."
